            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I based this alias.html on https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/blob/master/tpl/tplimpl/embedded/templates/alias.html. It seems like `.OutputFormats.Canonical` is v0.155+, so I bumped Hugo in CI to 0.156.0.",
